Hi All,

Here&#39;s my take.or 2 cents worth..:-)



Share your files all clipped without the garbage for others to listen to.
Save your original files for further development and records, in the case a
scientific organization wants to &quot;hear&quot; the original along with the clipped,
walahh you have both. And everyone is Happy!

LK



