&gt; a lot clearer, i also now see a couple sections of just noise that 
&gt; don&#39;t belong and eliminate them from the mix. You can&#39;t piece these 
&gt; files together to make something it&#39;s not, so i keep them in true 
&gt; form pretty much to the original.

&gt; -Steve

